\section{Language identifiers}\label{languagecodes}

The following wxLanguage constants may be used to specify the language
in \helpref{wxLocale::Init}{wxlocaleinit} and are returned by 
\helpref{wxLocale::GetSystemLanguage}{wxlocalegetsystemlanguage}:
